'''Alexandro Maidana Mendieta''' (born 26 July 2005) is a Paraguayan professional [[association football|football]] player who plays as a [[left-back]] for [[Argentine Primera División]] club [[Talleres de Córdoba|Talleres]], and  the [[Paraguay national football team|Paraguay national team]].

==Club career==
A youth product of [[Club Guaraní|Guaraní]], Maidana began his senior career in 2023 on loan with [[Atyrá F.C.|Atyrá]] in the [[Paraguayan División Intermedia]]. The following season, he went on loan with [[Resistencia S.C.|Resistencia]] in the same division.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.lavoz.com.ar/deportes/lateral-izquierdo-paraguayo-llegaria-talleres-alexandro-maidana_0_HMBe8ww8al.html|title=El lateral izquierdo paraguayo que llegaría a Talleres: quién es Alexandro Maidana|first=Javier|last=Flores|date=27 February 2026|website=www.lavoz.com.ar}}</ref> In 2025, he returned to Guaraní and played for their senior team in the [[Paraguayan Primera División]]. On 27 February 2026, he transferred to the [[Argentine Primera División]] club [[Talleres de Córdoba|Talleres]] on a long-term contract.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.abc.com.py/deportes/futbol/guarani/2026/02/27/alexandro-maidana-deja-el-legendario-para-sumarse-a-talleres-de-cordoba/|title=Alexandro Maidana deja el "Legendario" para sumarse a Talleres de Córdoba - Guaraní - ABC Color|website=www.abc.com.py}}</ref>

==International career==
Maidana was part of the  [[Paraguay national under-20 football team|Paraguay U20]]s at the [[2025 FIFA U-20 World Cup]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.abc.com.py/deportes/futbol/guarani/2025/08/07/guarani-maidana-sensible-resta-legendaria/|title=Guaraní: Maidana, sensible resta legendaria - Guaraní - ABC Color|website=www.abc.com.py}}</ref> He was called up to the senior [[Paraguay national football team|Paraguay national team]] for a set of friendlies in March 2026.<ref>{{cite news |title=Andrés Cubas, lesión y baja en Paraguay: entra Lucas Romero |url=https://www.abc.com.py/deportes/futbol/seleccion-paraguaya/2026/03/20/andres-cubas-lesion-y-baja-en-paraguay-fue-llamado/ |access-date=20 March 2026 |work=www.abc.com.py |date=20 March 2026 |language=es}}</ref> He debuted in a friendly 1–0 win over [[Greece national football team|Greece]] on 26 March 2026.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://canalshowsport.com.ar/alexandro-maidana-debuto-con-paraguay-y-suena-con-ir-al-mundial/|title=Alexandro Maidana debutó con Paraguay y sueña con ir al Mundial marzo 2026 - Canal Showsport|date=28 March 2026}}</ref>

